Package hms.admin

Class StaffManagement

Object
StaffManagement
public class StaffManagement extends Object
Manages staff members in the hospital system. Provides functionalities for viewing, adding, updating, and removing staff members.

  • Method Details

    • viewStaff

      public void viewStaff(List<Map<String,String>> staffList, String role, String gender, int minAge, int maxAge)
      Displays a filtered list of staff based on role, gender, and age range.
      Parameters:
      staffList - The list of staff records.
      role - The role to filter by (e.g., "Doctor"). Pass null or empty for no filtering.
      gender - The gender to filter by (e.g., "Male"). Pass null or empty for no filtering.
      minAge - The minimum age for filtering.
      maxAge - The maximum age for filtering.

    • addStaff

      public void addStaff(List<Map<String,String>> staffList, String id, String name, String role, String gender, String age)
      Adds a new staff member to the list if the ID is unique.
      Parameters:
      staffList - The list of staff records.
      id - The unique ID of the new staff member.
      name - The name of the staff member.
      role - The role of the staff member (e.g., "Doctor").
      gender - The gender of the staff member.
      age - The age of the staff member.

    • updateStaff

      public void updateStaff(List<Map<String,String>> staffList, String id, String name, String role, String gender, String age, String choiceUpdate)
      Updates the details of an existing staff member.
      Parameters:
      staffList - The list of staff records.
      id - The unique ID of the staff member to update.
      name - The new name of the staff member.
      role - The new role of the staff member.
      gender - The new gender of the staff member.
      age - The new age of the staff member.
      choiceUpdate - The field to update ("Name", "Role", "Gender", "Age", or "E" for all fields).

    • removeStaff

      Removes a staff member from the list based on their ID.
      Parameters:
      staffList - The list of staff records.
      id - The unique ID of the staff member to remove.
